  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CannotModifyArchivedEntity
    The rejection thrown when a request for modification of an entity cannot be satisfied because the entity is marked as `archived`.
    CannotModifyDeletedEntity
    The rejection thrown when a request for modification of an entity cannot be satisfied because the entity is marked as `deleted`.
    EntityAlreadyArchived
    The rejection thrown when a request to mark the entity as `archived` is received for the already archived entity.
    EntityAlreadyDeleted
    The rejection thrown when a request to mark the entity as `deleted` is received for the entity which is already marked as `deleted`.
